claim.claim-text:
18. A method of fabricating a liner assembly, said method comprising the steps of:
a. assembling a face sheet including a first plurality of openings over a noise attenuation structure, said face sheet including a seam formed by adjacent portions of the face sheet;
b. covering the seam with a retainer;
c. bonding the retainer to the face sheet with an adhesive; and
d. forming a second plurality of openings through the retainer and the adhesive to communicate noise energy to said noise attenuation structure.
